  "description": "Maximum shimmer (0.85) plus significant frost (0.62) simultaneously — the crystalline high-frequency architecture at its peak expression. Approximately 85% of grains receive an octave-up pitch shift. The frost detuning adds crystalline harshness above the shimmer. A single sine source granularized into a prismatic spectrum. OPAL's signature sound taken to its maximum.",
